    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented in museum-grade condition, this E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp via individual throttle bodies and a precision-gated Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including reinforced subframe mounts, a complete VANOS overhaul, and rod bearing replacement to ensure mechanical longevity. The suspension remains taut with factory-spec bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the variable M differential lock provides optimal torque distribution. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the chassis rigidity and engine harmonics remain as sharp as the day it left Regensburg. A peerless example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Full service records available. Low mileage.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true 'time capsule' specimen, maintained to the highest possible standard. Finished in a deep Metallic Charcoal, the paint remains in showroom condition, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled environment. There are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks on the body. Inside, the cabin retains its original scent; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear or creasing, and the dash and trim are free of any UV damage or scratches. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the heated seat elements, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively at the dealership with a comprehensive folder of maintenance records included. A major service was recently completed, including all fluid flushes and the installation of a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of road salt or fluid weeping. This sale includes both original master keys, the original window sticker, and a set of custom-fit all-weather floor liners. For the collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this vehicle offers a like-new driving experience.",
      "price": 44900.0,
